:2420221,"uid":51540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:17:07.000Z","msg":"樓主我嘅經歷同你好似但比你更加慘<br />\n我由細個有記憶開始已經係以淚洗面直到大個咗都係咁<br />\n呢兩年睇咗好多心理學嘅嘢先開始慢慢move on<br />\n我原本打咗一大篇文想覆你<br />\n不過諗諗吓都係算唔想鬥慘唔想放負<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之俾你嘅建議就係接受父母唔係無條件愛仔女嘅事實<br />\n同埋如果你屋企人係好難頂係你痛苦嘅根源，你擺脫唔到就唯有情感上detach<br />\n你對人好同付出之前，要睇下人地係咪值得你付出，好似你阿爸對你好你就對返佢好，你阿媽點對你你就點對佢，如果唔係嘅話你只係縱容緊一種toxic, unfair 嘅關係"},{"pid":"92db6a88dddc6a91611f8672e7691dd1363ced31","tid":2420221,"uid":255843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf90382ac222543af9c83c8655acb027a6d20dbe","tid":2420221,"uid":339937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8813e18d82fd890ca09f3ccc32657539b0556660","tid":2420221,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T20:31:13.000Z","msg":"佢試過有兩次想殺死我 有無問係咩事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T20:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T21:35:40.000Z","msg":"係咪產後抑鬱冇處理好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edc1b09a6646ffac355aaf9e2f7dd5082b557339","tid":2420221,"uid":7697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3cd5e2e3fffaa8073af0c37ffb5dc0ea94ae052e","tid":2420221,"uid":339937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdfba2d7a9f292e9632f5e308a39c7099234c000","tid":2420221,"uid":373951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf90382ac222543af9c83c8655acb027a6d20dbe","tid":2420221,"uid":339937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T20:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T20:41:24.000Z","msg":"唔信你D咩 做咩錯事要斬你"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T20:48:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T23:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset